Introduction

NCHIVE (Korean: 엔카이브; Japanese: ニチベ) is a six-member boy group under AUBEMOOON STUDIO. As seven, they debuted on April 9, 2024, with their single album "Drive".

On July 1, 2024, AUBEMOON STUDIO announced that Member Minjun has decided to leave NCHIVE due to health reasons.
